                                                                                              NIST SP 800-37, REVISION 2            RISK MANAGEMENT FRAMEWORK FOR INFORMATION SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS
                                                                                                                                                                       A System Life Cycle Approach for Security and Privacy
                                                                                              ________________________________________________________________________________________________

                                                                                              3.3 SELECT

                                                                                                                                                Purpose
                                                                                                    The purpose of the Select step is to select, tailor, and document the controls necessary to protect
                                                                                                    the information system and organization commensurate with risk to organizational operations
                                                                                                    and assets, individuals, other organizations, and the Nation.




                                                                                              SELECT TASKS
This publication is available free of charge from: https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.SP.800-37r2




                                                                                              Table 4 provides a summary of tasks and expected outcomes for the RMF Select step. Applicable
                                                                                              Cybersecurity Framework constructs are also provided.
                                                                                                                                  TABLE 4: SELECT TASKS AND OUTCOMES

                                                                                                                  Tasks                                               Outcomes
                                                                                               TASK S-1                                   • Control baselines necessary to protect the system commensurate
                                                                                               CONTROL SELECTION                            with risk are selected.
                                                                                                                                            [Cybersecurity Framework: Profile]
                                                                                               TASK S-2                                   • Controls are tailored producing tailored control baselines.
                                                                                               CONTROL TAILORING                            [Cybersecurity Framework: Profile]
                                                                                               TASK S-3                                   • Controls are designated as system-specific, hybrid, or common
                                                                                               CONTROL ALLOCATION                           controls.
                                                                                                                                          • Controls are allocated to the specific system elements (i.e.,
                                                                                                                                            machine, physical, or human elements).
                                                                                                                                            [Cybersecurity Framework: Profile; PR.IP]
                                                                                               TASK S-4                                   • Controls and associated tailoring actions are documented in
                                                                                               DOCUMENTATION OF PLANNED CONTROL             security and privacy plans or equivalent documents.
                                                                                               IMPLEMENTATIONS                              [Cybersecurity Framework: Profile]
                                                                                               TASK S-5                                   • A continuous monitoring strategy for the system that reflects the
                                                                                               CONTINUOUS MONITORING STRATEGY—              organizational risk management strategy is developed.
                                                                                               SYSTEM                                       [Cybersecurity Framework: ID.GV; DE.CM]
                                                                                               TASK S-6                                   • Security and privacy plans reflecting the selection of controls
                                                                                               PLAN REVIEW AND APPROVAL                     necessary to protect the system and the environment of
                                                                                                                                            operation commensurate with risk are reviewed and approved by
                                                                                                                                            the authorizing official.



                                                                                                      Quick link to summary table for RMF tasks, responsibilities, and supporting roles.

                                                                                              CONTROL SELECTION
                                                                                              TASK S-1 Select the controls for the system and the environment of operation.
                                                                                              Potential Inputs: Security categorization; organization- and system-level risk assessment results; system
                                                                                              element information; system component inventory; list of security and privacy requirements allocated to
                                                                                              the system, system elements, and environment of operation; list of contractual requirements allocated to
                                                                                              external providers of the system or system element; business impact analysis or criticality analysis; risk
                                                                                              management strategy; organizational security and privacy policy; federal or organization-approved or
                                                                                              mandated baselines or overlays; Cybersecurity Framework Profiles.



